{"tid":1631932,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"6月堆p牌呢家已經甩晒P","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T12:33:49.000Z","uid":761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b5810e4010f25e7e5c285d346861f9dceca39979","tid":1631932,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"連登被大量滲透"},{"pid":"b44695822b615cb6f97193d8d6fda7fcb7c00ec3","tid":1631932,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:38.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"91fdb91e1737b2a8cb522216dcabe7757840b3c0","tid":1631932,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:26.000Z","msg":"唔好分化p牌。<br />\nCD-rom如我都係嬲到要發聲先上黎"},{"pid":"fb3ab07af52fb3e6458d24fd22b4e4aeecec73fb","tid":1631932,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5810e4010f25e7e5c285d346861f9dceca39979","tid":1631932,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"連登被大量滲透"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:36.000Z","msg":"未<br />\n6月之後暫時都係p牌"},{"pid":"d5f226df0cf3db5f55ad0ffd513caf38e57d937a","tid":1631932,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5519d3b97c1fb55bf8c24b062aeb81548a139c","tid":1631932,"uid":331524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:43.000Z","msg":"仲P牌緊揮手區"},{"pid":"aa5079ace194a83e64d821144e0b87e2634fb82e","tid":1631932,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:46:29.000Z","msg":"我又揮<br />\n本諗住做CD-ROM算<br />\n頂唔順先開AC F"},{"pid":"b37634ca024612dc5da1e332a01dd936c418ce50","tid":1631932,"uid":288803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:40:10.000Z","msg":"6月12覺醒日仲未甩"},{"pid":"70329a8b5060864b7ff86ca6ed3fe9e3bef67a02","tid":1631932,"uid":278858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"25字頭都未甩p"}]}